@startuml interactive_extras
title Overlay and ADR

participant "Software Architect" as architect
participant "Interactive" as bausteinsicht_cli_interactive
participant "Overlay" as bausteinsicht_overlay
participant "Document" as bausteinsicht_drawio_document
participant "Loader" as bausteinsicht_model_loader

architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_interactive : 1. bausteinsicht overlay apply ‑‑metric health
bausteinsicht_cli_interactive -> bausteinsicht_overlay : 2. apply(view, metric): color elements by score
bausteinsicht_overlay -> bausteinsicht_drawio_document : 3. write heatmap fill colors onto the diagram
bausteinsicht_overlay --> architect : 4. overlay applied (removable via overlay remove)
architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_interactive : 5. bausteinsicht adr new 'Use JSONC for the DSL'
bausteinsicht_cli_interactive -> bausteinsicht_model_loader : 6. scaffold ADR-NNN-Name.adoc from the Nygard template
bausteinsicht_cli_interactive --> architect : 7. new ADR file ready for editing

@enduml
